<l n="59">os llid aberis lledwc</l> <l n="60">oeddwn wann i ddwyn i wc</l> <l n="61">beth bynac fo /r/ kymro kain</l> <l n="62">o niwaid i nai owain</l> <l n="63">mi awn ar gam y mod</l> <l n="64">adde kam adwc kymod</l> <l n="65">arched merch Ednyved naf</l> <l n="66">Ym heddwch mi ai haeddaf</l> <l n="67">howel Jevangk hil owain</l> <l n="68">yw /r/ ail nerth ar ol i nain</l> <l n="69">ac ato down pe i gedtid </l> <l n="70">i vwrw llwyth o var a llid</l> <l n="71">ac ni ddoe wc Ievan ddoeth</l> <l n="72">ar fynghefn a {<del>a</del>}er vynghyfoeth</l> </lg> <lg type="olnod"> <l>Gvto or glynn ai kant</l> </lg> </div> <div type="nodiadau" xml:id="LlGC3051D_106nodiadau"> <div type="cym"> <note type="trefn_cym">1&ndash;34, i.1&ndash;4 (o bosibl mewn llaw ddiweddarach), 35&ndash;72.</note> <note type="llaw_cym">llaw anhysbys (X123)</note> <note type="dyddiad_cym"><hi rend="italics">c</hi>.1579</note> <note type="nodiadau_trawsysgrifiad_cym" >i.1&ndash;4&nbsp;&nbsp;Ychwanegwyd y llinellau hyn ar ymyl y ddalen, gan bin teneuach. Mae’n bosibl eu bod yn yr un llaw &acirc;’r testun.</note> <note type="nodiadau_trawsysgrifiad_cym">41&nbsp;&nbsp;Torrwyd brig tudalen 153 a chollwyd diwedd y llinell.</note> </div> <div type="eng"> <note type="trefn_eng">1&ndash;34, i.1&ndash;4 (perhaps in a later hand), 35&ndash;72.</note> <note type="llaw_eng">unknown hand (X123)</note> <note type="dyddiad_eng"><hi rend="italics">c</hi>.1579</note> <note type="nodiadau_trawsysgrifiad_eng" >i.1&ndash;4&nbsp;&nbsp;These lines were added in the margin by a thinner pen. It is possible that they are in the same hand as the text.</note> <note type="nodiadau_trawsysgrifiad_eng">41&nbsp;&nbsp;The top of page 153 was cut and the end of the line was lost.</note> </div> </div> </div> <div type="lev3" xml:id="LlGC3056D_106"> <div xml:id="LlGC3056D_106testun"> <head>LlGC 3056D, 152&ndash;4</head> <pb n="152_llgc_1438101"/> <gap reason="sampling"/> <lg type="nodyn_brig"> <l>k’ i ofyn kymod Ienn’ vychan</l> <